    <p class="kicker">What it actually is</p>
    <p class="statement">An international transfer is <em>not a long-haul taxi</em>. It is an agreed chain: a car in Brazil, a border crossing under the rules of the specific country, a car and driver on the other side (or a single car for the whole route — where allowed), passenger documents, timing, and a fallback scenario.</p>
